What does it run on?
--------------------

This suite of programs has been tested on Atari STM/FM, Mega ST (TOS 1.2,
1.4) and TT (TOS 3.05) series of computers running MiNT 0.91, 0.92, 0.93,
0.94, 0.95, 0.96 up to 1.10 with many patches. The baud rate of the serial
ports can only be set by getty under MiNT versions 0.95 and above and will
only work properly for the TT's extra ports from version 1.05 and above.

Stephen Usher 10th September, 1994.

